Grammar

    0 $accept: Program $end

    1 Program: Decls

    2 Decls: Decls Decl
    3      | ε

    4 Decl: FuncDecl
    5     | VarDecl
    6     | TypeDecl

    7 FuncDecl: VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON
    8         | VarType IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ParamList RPARENTHESES FuncBody

    9 FuncBody: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   10 VarDecl: VarType VarList SEMICOLON

   11 TypeDecl: _VarType SEMICOLON

   12 VarType: _VarType
   13        | CONST _VarType

   14 _VarType: BuiltinType
   15         | STRUCT IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   16         | UNION IDENTIFIER LBRACE FieldDecls RBRACE
   17         | ENUM IDENTIFIER LBRACE EnumList RBRACE
   18         | _VarType ASTERISK
   19         | IDENTIFIER

   20 VarList: VarList COMMA VarInit
   21        | VarInit
   22        | ε

   23 VarInit: IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList
   24        | IDENTIFIER ArrayBoundList ASSIGN Expr

   25 ArrayBoundList: ArrayBoundList ArrayBound
   26               | ArrayBound
   27               | ε

   28 ArrayBound: LBRACKET INTEGER RBRACKET

   29 ParamList: ParamList COMMA Param
   30          | ParamList COMMA ELLIPSES
   31          | Param
   32          | ELLIPSES
   33          | ε

   34 Param: VarType IDENTIFIER
   35      | VarType

   36 BuiltinType: CHAR
   37            | SHORT
   38            | INT
   39            | LONG
   40            | UNSIGNED
   41            | UNSIGNED CHAR
   42            | UNSIGNED SHORT
   43            | UNSIGNED INT
   44            | UNSIGNED LONG
   45            | FLOAT
   46            | DOUBLE
   47            | BOOL
   48            | VOID

   49 FieldDecls: FieldDecls FieldDecl
   50           | ε

   51 FieldDecl: VarType MemberList SEMICOLON
   52          | SEMICOLON

   53 MemberList: MemberList COMMA IDENTIFIER
   54           | IDENTIFIER
   55           | ε

   56 EnumList: EnumList COMMA Enum
   57         | Enum
   58         | ε

   59 Enum: IDENTIFIER
   60     | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN INTEGER

   61 Stmts: Stmts Stmt
   62      | ε

   63 Stmt: Expr SEMICOLON
   64     | IfStmt
   65     | SwitchStmt
   66     | ForStmt
   67     | DoStmt
   68     | WhileStmt
   69     | ContinueStmt
   70     | BreakStmt
   71     | ReturnStmt
   72     | Block
   73     | TypeDecl
   74     | VarDecl
   75     | SEMICOLON

   76 IfStmt: IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt ELSE Stmt
   77       | IF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   78 SwitchStmt: SWITCH LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES LBRACE CaseStmtList RBRACE

   79 CaseStmtList: CaseStmtList CaseStmt
   80             | ε

   81 CaseStmt: CASE Expr COLON Stmts
   82         | DEFAULT COLON Stmts

   83 ForStmt: FOR LPARENTHESES Expr SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   84        | FOR LPARENTHESES SEMICOLON Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt
   85        | FOR LPARENTHESES VarDecl Expr SEMICOLON Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   86 DoStmt: DO Stmt WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES SEMICOLON

   87 WhileStmt: WHILE LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES Stmt

   88 ContinueStmt: CONTINUE SEMICOLON

   89 BreakStmt: BREAK SEMICOLON

   90 ReturnStmt: RETURN SEMICOLON
   91           | RETURN Expr SEMICOLON

   92 Block: LBRACE Stmts RBRACE

   93 Expr: IDENTIFIER
   94     | Constant
   95     | LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
   96     | Expr COMMA Expr
   97     | IDENTIFIER LPARENTHESES ExprList RPARENTHESES
   98     | Expr DOT IDENTIFIER
   99     | Expr ARROW IDENTIFIER
  100     | Expr LBRACKET Expr RBRACKET
  101     | LPARENTHESES VarType RPARENTHESES Expr
  102     | SIZEOF LPARENTHESES VarType RPARENTHESES
  103     | SIZEOF LPARENTHESES Expr RPARENTHESES
  104     | SIZEOF LPARENTHESES IDENTIFIER RPARENTHESES
  105     | ADD Expr
  106     | SUB Expr
  107     | ASTERISK Expr
  108     | AMPERSAND Expr
  109     | Expr ASSIGN Expr
  110     | Expr ADD Expr
  111     | Expr SUB Expr
  112     | Expr ASTERISK Expr
  113     | Expr DIV Expr
  114     | Expr MOD Expr
  115     | Expr DADD
  116     | Expr DSUB
